{"id":2875,"date":"2024-03-22T16:13:10","date_gmt":"2024-03-22T09:13:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2875"},"modified":"2024-03-22T16:13:10","modified_gmt":"2024-03-22T09:13:10","slug":"truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do-tang-laptop-cho-tan-sinh-vien-2024","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do-tang-laptop-cho-tan-sinh-vien-2024\/","title":{"rendered":"TR\u01af\u1edcNG \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC TH\u00c0NH \u0110\u00d4 T\u1eb6NG LAPTOP CHO T\u00c2N SINH VI\u00caN 2024"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m 20 n\u0103m th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng Laptop v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh cho T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean 2024.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_20752\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-20752\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-20752\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/HB_2024_Laptop2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2037\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-20752\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 t\u1eb7ng Laptop cho T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean 2024<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>D\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 15\/4\/2024 &#8211; 15\/5\/2024:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">80 Laptop Samsung, tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 10.000.000 VN\u0110\/ su\u1ea5t<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed K\u00fd t\u00fac x\u00e1 n\u0103m h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 12.000.000 VN\u0110<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Cam k\u1ebft vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m sau t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Sinh vi\u00ean \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ch\u00ednh quy 2024, \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 15\/4\/2024 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y 15\/5\/2024<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed 7.200.000 VN\u0110 tr\u01b0\u1edbc 15\/05\/2024 <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f9 tr\u1eeb v\u00e0o h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed k\u1ef3 1 khi th\u00ed sinh nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c)<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>D\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 20\/5\/2024 &#8211; 30\/6\/2024:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_20750\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-20750\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-20750\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/HB_2024_Laptop1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2037\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-20750\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 t\u1eb7ng Laptop cho T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean 2024<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">65 Laptop Samsung, tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 10.000.000 VN\u0110\/ su\u1ea5t<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Cam k\u1ebft vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m sau t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Sinh vi\u00ean \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ch\u00ednh quy 2024, \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 20\/05\/2024 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y 30\/06\/2024<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed 7.200.000 VN\u0110 tr\u01b0\u1edbc 30\/06\/2024 <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f9 tr\u1eeb v\u00e0o h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed k\u1ef3 1 khi th\u00ed sinh nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c)<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><b>*Ghi ch\u00fa<\/b><b>: <\/b><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ri\u00eang sinh vi\u00ean Ng\u00e0nh D\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc th\u1eddi gian t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 20\/5\/2024 &#8211; 30\/6\/2024, sau th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m x\u1ebfp lo\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc l\u1ef1c l\u1edbp 12.<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u0103m 2024, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o 14 ng\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc thu\u1ed9c 4 nh\u00f3m ng\u00e0nh, trong \u0111\u00f3 2 ng\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc m\u1edbi Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef Trung Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ecdc. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c em h\u1ecdc sinh THPT, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_20159\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-20159\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-20159 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Banner-DHCQ2024-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"948\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-20159\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 tuy\u1ec3n sinh \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc 2024 v\u1edbi 14 ng\u00e0nh thu\u1ed9c 4 nh\u00f3m ng\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, Kinh t\u1ebf &#8211; Lu\u1eadt, Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef &#8211; KHXH v\u00e0 S\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 &#8211; m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o theo \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng, ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 Thadoer ti\u1ebfp theo v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Top c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc t\u01b0 th\u1ee5c h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ASEAN (AppliedHE)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean xanh, kho\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea1t, trong l\u00e0nh; h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc th\u00f4ng minh, s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi, nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111a n\u0103ng, b\u1ec3 b\u01a1i, h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng &#8211; Doanh nghi\u1ec7p, sinh vi\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">95% sinh vi\u00ean TDD c\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m ngay sau khi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Sinh vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, t\u1ef1 tin th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 thao, v\u0103n h\u00f3a, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed \u0111a d\u1ea1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp THPT 2023 (x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n h\u1ecdc b\u1ea1) \u0111\u1ee3t 1 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y 30\/04\/2024:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp THPT:<\/span>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 1, h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 2 l\u1edbp 11 v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 1 l\u1edbp 12 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1eeb 18 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ba m\u00f4n x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n l\u1edbp 12 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1eeb 18 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1edf l\u00ean\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nhanh ch\u00f3ng g\u1eedi h\u1ed3 s\u01a1, \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Thadoer th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u1eadn Laptop v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng qu\u00e0 t\u1eb7ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1eeb Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd:<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>* C\u00e1ch 1: Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n ph\u00e1t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec7n<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng Trung t\u00e2m Tuy\u1ec3n sinh \u2013 Hotline: 0934.078.668, 02433.861.601<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ea7ng 1, Nh\u00e0 A, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Km 15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>* C\u00e1ch 2: Tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Website:<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/<\/span><\/a><\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fanpage:<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo<\/span><\/a><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m 20 n\u0103m th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng Laptop v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh cho T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean 2024. D\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 15\/4\/2024 &#8211; 15\/5\/2024: 80 Laptop Samsung, tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 10.000.000 VN\u0110\/ su\u1ea5t Mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed K\u00fd t\u00fac x\u00e1 n\u0103m [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":9,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[36,1,20],"tags":[109,110,42,125],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2875"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tu